metadata.name: Open from the inside out
metadata.description: I exist here. Inside this art, it is my home and also me. Would you like to come in, to my mind for a cup of tears? There is a reason for everything and an answer but not all are known. See me, hear me, I was silent for so long. Lets waft the musk of reality and indulge in the bliss of existence. Gaining freedom one NFT at a time, making my way out of the jar which I yield captivity, from the inside out.
